{"schema_version":"1.7.3","id":"OESA-2025-2786","published":"2025-12-05T13:12:32Z","modified":"2025-12-05T13:33:10.285252Z","upstream":["CVE-2025-60753"],"summary":"libarchive security update","details":"is an open-source BSD-licensed C programming library that  provides streaming access to a variety of different archive formats, including tar, cpio, pax, zip, and ISO9660 images. The distribution  also includes bsdtar and bsdcpio, full-featured implementations of  tar and cpio that use .\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nAn issue was discovered in libarchive bsdtar before version 3.8.1 in function apply_substitution in file tar/subst.c when processing crafted -s substitution rules. This can cause unbounded memory allocation and lead to denial of service (Out-of-Memory crash).(CVE-2025-60753)","affected":[{"package":{"name":"libarchive","ecosystem":"openEuler:22.03-LTS-SP4","purl":"pkg:rpm/openEuler/libarchive&distro=openEuler-22.03-LTS-SP4"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4"}]}],"ecosystem_specific":{"aarch64":["bsdcat-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.aarch64.rpm","bsdcpio-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.aarch64.rpm","bsdtar-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.aarch64.rpm","libarchive-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.aarch64.rpm","libarchive-debuginfo-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.aarch64.rpm","libarchive-debugsource-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.aarch64.rpm","libarchive-devel-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.aarch64.rpm"],"noarch":["libarchive-help-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.noarch.rpm"],"src":["libarchive-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.src.rpm"],"x86_64":["bsdcat-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.x86_64.rpm","bsdcpio-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.x86_64.rpm","bsdtar-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.x86_64.rpm","libarchive-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.x86_64.rpm","libarchive-debuginfo-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.x86_64.rpm","libarchive-debugsource-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.x86_64.rpm","libarchive-devel-3.5.2-10.oe2203sp4.x86_64.rpm"]},"database_specific":{"source":"https://repo.openeuler.org/security/data/osv/OESA-2025-2786.json"}}],"references":[{"type":"ADVISORY","url":"https://www.openeuler